{"tid":2332961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨軍：一名駐守警察總部的女文職人員初步確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-12-20T04:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T05:02:56.000Z","uid":21470,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ce929155a7c517cd9c16eeb01140fe64db15554b","tid":2332961,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:54:03.000Z","msg":"警務處一名女文職人員初步確診2019冠狀病毒病<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  一名駐守警察總部的女文職人員初步確診2019冠狀病毒病。她於十二月十八日感到不適求診，並進行檢測。經測試後，她昨日（十二月十九日）得知對2019冠狀病毒病病毒測試呈陽性反應。該名文職人員於過去十四日沒有外遊記錄，並沒有與公眾接觸，工作期間亦有佩戴口罩，她最後一日上班日為十二月十六日。<br />\n<br />\n  警方高度關注事件，並有以下訊息：<br />\n<br />\n  （一）在等候衞生署進一步評估及建議前，與該名人員可能有緊密接觸的警務人員及文職人員，均獲安排接受檢疫及病毒檢測；<br />\n<br />\n  （二）警方已即時派員清潔及消毒該名人員的相關工作地方；<br />\n<br />\n  （三）警方亦經常提醒同事注意個人衞生，減少社交接觸，減低傳染風險，如有任何不適，須立即呈報並求醫；以及<br />\n<br />\n  （四）警方會靈活調派人手，確保相關緊急服務不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n  警方將會繼續與衞生署保持緊密聯繫，主動提供該名文職人員的近日工作記錄等資料，以及安排相關密切接觸者進入檢疫中心接受檢疫。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年12月20日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間12時37分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/20/P2020122000314.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F20%2FP2020122000314.htm&d=XkDMRo5st5VLQkVJYuplWLTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=dde96a80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/20/P2020122000314.htm</a>"},{"pid":"753450c54fc7468e0d7ff84838bac5e6876b0b06","tid":2332961,"uid":12171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QH0LNE7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQH0LNE7.gif&h=32e3cbae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KOaeki.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KOaeki.gif&h=0b564bbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5911762314f4ddc8febbe01e2412d9afdd103450","tid":2332961,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8c1a19b0165657494ef3f020917ba2652e2fd9","tid":2332961,"uid":201512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"黑警群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a21ac6ff843468f8e8b07bd4b225101342d8c1e","tid":2332961,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"死全警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4781c5b355955b7e39ce0ddf32001668e30584df","tid":2332961,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">痛快</span>"},{"pid":"d73b466d4f813fe6fc603871fc575a0c0ff233cf","tid":2332961,"uid":12171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XoJ2Bt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XoJ2Bt.gif&h=836520b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43673417583da86e4f02f181dfe336bd4fcc8db4","tid":2332961,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:01:56.000Z","msg":"死全家未呀"},{"pid":"98ee6620b1a458695c23cb80f9fbb4704aeba857","tid":2332961,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:02:56.000Z","msg":"文職即係ACO/CA/PS啦<br />\nEO/AP會講明職系"}]}